'''犀鳥目'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|Bucerotiformes}}）是鳥類分類中的一個目，包括[[犀鳥|犀鳥]]、[[地犀鳥|地犀鳥]]、[[戴勝|戴勝]]及[[林戴勝|林戴勝]]等物種<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://tolweb.org/Bucerotiformes/26427 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2019-05-04 |archive-date=2017-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170108095733/http://tolweb.org/Bucerotiformes/26427 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，過去曾將此目物種歸於[[佛法僧目|佛法僧目]]中，但有愈來愈多的証明建議應獨立分類<ref>{{cite journal |title=Molecular support for a sister group relationship between Pici and Galbulae (Piciformes ''sensu'' Wetmore 1960) |journal=[[Journal_of_Avian_Biology|J. Avian Biol.]] |year=2003 |first1=Ulf S. |last1=Johansson |first2=Per G.P. |last2=Ericson |volume=34 |issue=2 |pages=185–197 |doi=10.1034/j.1600-048X.2003.03103.x |url=http://www.nrm.se/download/18.4e32c81078a8d9249800021325/Johansson%2520&%2520Ericson%2520-%2520Piciformes%5B1%5D.pdf |format= |accessdate=2008-10-30 |archive-date=2018-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181004210235/http://www.nrm.se/download/18.4e32c81078a8d9249800021325/Johansson%2520%26%2520Ericson%2520-%2520Piciformes%5B1%5D.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>Yuri, T. ''et al.'' (2013) [http://www.mdpi.com/2079-7737/2/1/419 Parsimony and Model-Based Analyses of Indels in Avian Nuclear Genes Reveal Congruent and Incongruent Phylogenetic Signals] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mdpi.com/2079-7737/2/1/419 |date=20161103001146 }}. ''Biology'', 2(1):419-444. doi:10.3390/biology2010419</ref><ref>Jarvis, E.D. ''et al''. (2014) [http://www.sciencemag.org/content/346/6215/1320.abstract Whole-genome analyses resolve early branches in the tree of life of modern birds] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sciencemag.org/content/346/6215/1320.abstract |date=20150924170848 }}. ''Science'', 346(6215):1320-1331.</ref>。

==系統發生學==
本目除了有常見的[[犀鳥科|犀鳥科]]及[[地犀鳥科|地犀鳥科]]物種外，近年的共識亦將[[戴勝科|戴勝科]]及[[林戴勝科|林戴勝科]]的物種歸於此目中<ref>{{cite web|last1=Gill|first1=Frank|last2=Donsker|first2=David|title=Todies, motmots, bee-eaters, hoopoes, wood hoopoes & hornbills|url=http://www.worldbirdnames.org/bow/todies/|website=IOC World Bird List v7.1|accessdate=31 March 2017|doi=10.14344/IOC.ML.7.1|archive-date=2020-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114205120/https://www.worldbirdnames.org/bow/todies/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。戴勝科及林戴勝科物種關係一直密切，其中包括它們共同擁有相同而獨特的[[鐙骨|鐙骨]]所致<ref>{{cite journal|last=Feduccia|first=Alan|year=1975|title=The Bony Stapes in the Upupidae and Phoeniculidae: Evidence for Common Ancestry|journal=The Wilson Bulletin|volume=87|issue=3|pages=416–417|url=http://sora.unm.edu/sites/default/files/journals/wilson/v087n03/p0416-p0417.pdf|access-date=2019-05-06|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411021430/https://sora.unm.edu/sites/default/files/journals/wilson/v087n03/p0416-p0417.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。過去在[[鳥類DNA分類系統|鳥類DNA分類系統]]中也有將戴勝科及林戴勝科獨立成戴勝目的建議
<ref name="Mayr">{{cite journal|last=Mayr|first=Gerald|year=2000|title=Tiny Hoopoe-Like Birds from the Middle Eocene of Messel (Germany)|journal=Auk|volume=117|issue=4|pages=964–970|doi=10.1642/0004-8038(2000)117[0964:THLBFT]2.0.CO;2|url=http://sora.unm.edu/node/26294|access-date=2019-05-06|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411021443/https://sora.unm.edu/node/26294|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 

近年的基因研究顯示[[地犀鳥科|地犀鳥科]]及[[犀鳥科|犀鳥科]]中的[[噪犀鳥屬|噪犀鳥屬]]形成一演化支以獨立出來<ref>Woodruff, D. S. & Srikwan, S. 2011. Molecular genetics and the conservation of hornbills in fragmented landscapes. In Poonswad, P. (ed) The Asian Hornbills: Ecology and Conservation. National Center for Genetic Engineering and Biotechnology, Bangkok, pp. 257-264.</ref>。這演化支代表早期的非洲世系，而其他則代表亞洲世系。

戴勝科中一直只有一科一屬一現存種，但近年已將從前的兩個亞種提升為[[非洲戴勝|非洲戴勝]]及[[馬達加斯加戴勝|馬達加斯加戴勝]]兩個物種<ref>Fry, C. Hilary (2003). "Wood-hoopoes". In Perrins, Christopher. The Firefly Encyclopedia of Birds. Firefly Books. p. 383. {{ISBN|1-55297-777-3}}.</ref>。

